title: Batman - The Telltale Series for iPhone/iPad (v1.1.0)
description:
Batman - The Telltale Series

Description

*NOTE: Recommended Devices for the best gameplay experience - iPhone 6 and up, iPad Mini 4 and up, iPad Air 2 and up, and iPad Pro - also requires iOS 8.0 and up. *

Enter the fractured psyche of Bruce Wayne and discover the powerful and far-reaching consequences of your choices as the Dark Knight.

In this gritty and violent new story from the award-winning creators of The Walking Dead â€“ A Telltale Games Series, you'll make discoveries that will shatter Bruce Wayne's world, and the already fragile stability of a corrupt Gotham City.

Your actions and your choices will determine the fate of the Batman.

Includes Episode 1 in this all-new series from the award-winning studio, Telltale Games
